animation raiderWalking
keyframe frame1 of duration 0.15 s
rotate arm_r 45 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l -45 degrees around x-axis 
rotate leg_r -45 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l 45 degrees around x-axis 

keyframe frame2 of duration 0.3 s
rotate arm_r -90 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l 90 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_r 90 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l -90 degrees around x-axis 

keyframe frame3 of duration 0.3 s
rotate arm_r 90 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l -90 degrees around x-axis 
rotate leg_r -90 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l 90 degrees around x-axis
repeat from frame2

keyframe final of duration 0.5 s
end animation